{"text_id":158254,"tokens":["Distance"," learning"," is"," a"," form"," of"," learning"," that"," involves"," attending"," classes"," from"," home",","," via"," online"," or"," video"," conferencing"," platforms",","," instead"," of"," attending"," them"," in"," person","."," There"," are"," both"," advantages"," and"," disadvantages"," to"," the"," concept",","," and"," it"," is"," up"," for"," debate"," whether"," or"," not"," students"," would"," benefit"," from"," having"," the"," option"," to"," learn"," remotely",".","\n","The"," primary"," advantages"," of"," distance"," learning"," taught"," by"," schools"," are"," that"," students"," can"," be"," taught"," from"," virtually"," anywhere"," in"," the"," world"," and"," save"," money"," on"," transportation"," costs",","," as"," well"," as"," the"," cost"," of"," textbooks","."," Additionally",","," they"," can"," learn"," at"," their"," own"," pace",","," providing"," more"," flexibility"," and"," convenience"," in"," their"," education",","," without"," having"," to"," sacrifice"," quality",".","\n","On"," the"," other"," hand",","," there"," are"," also"," disadvantages"," to"," distance"," learning","."," Students"," can"," lack"," the"," motivation"," they"," have"," when"," learning"," in"," person",","," and"," it"," is"," difficult"," to"," create"," a"," sense"," of"," community",","," which"," is"," key"," for"," learning"," and"," integrating"," with"," peers","."," Additionally",","," learning"," in"," a"," virtual"," learning"," environment"," can"," lead"," to"," isolation",","," which"," can"," further"," lead"," to"," feeling"," disconnected"," and"," create"," a"," lack"," of"," engagement",".","\n","In"," my"," opinion",","," distance"," learning"," can"," be"," beneficial",","," but"," it"," depends"," on"," the"," person"," and"," their"," circumstances","."," For"," mature"," and"," independent"," students"," that"," are"," able"," to"," work"," independently",","," it"," can"," definitely